{"tid":1671924,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係頂唔順番工啲三姑六婆","createTime":"2019-10-23T20:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T16:07:32.000Z","uid":99653,"like":66,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9856487abcf49d4f944e094bf08ee4c4740ec8a0","tid":1671924,"uid":99653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:27:59.000Z","msg":"我明白係社會上有一定嘅social能力係好重要<br />\n但係係咪真係一番到工就要埋班三姑六婆堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一唔埋堆 佢地講個個就會係你<br />\n真係好辛苦 <br />\n好似番工social多過做野咁<br />\n<br />\n利申絲 份工男多過女 <br />\n啲男人真係易相處過大部分我個度嘅女人好多<br />\n所以會同男同事close啲<br />\n同女同事相處成日都要諗自己有冇啲咩得罪佢地<br />\n要小心翼翼咁講野<br />\n所以有時感覺會冇咁熱情 疏離啲<br />\n好驚比佢地係背後話我成日痴住啲仔<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 次次番完工都會失眠 諗好多野"},{"pid":"82c0317a9e4c1f818bf393e15e58baa21886bc25","tid":1671924,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25ff174fb21e29e30b3eb7d37214c0f5da2ca4c4","tid":1671924,"uid":99653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"82c0317a9e4c1f818bf393e15e58baa21886bc25","tid":1671924,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:54:43.000Z","msg":"心底裏係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但番到工點都局住扮social<br />\n成日都做緊唔係自己嘅自己真係好痛苦"},{"pid":"060a71cc8722c5b5b6a97d973aa17d75e431c9c9","tid":1671924,"uid":123787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T21:00:42.000Z","msg":"辭職搵過第2份啦<br />\n人生苦短，聽你咁講你都唔多想做呢份"},{"pid":"d256e3b37eb161c7a5914097f56027bc5f75d6eb","tid":1671924,"uid":99653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"060a71cc8722c5b5b6a97d973aa17d75e431c9c9","tid":1671924,"uid":123787,"like":3,"dislik